AVERMEDIA INFO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 53.77% to NT$167,445,000 from NT$362,192,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            167,445          362,192    
YOY%             -53.77%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            581,713         1,137,846   
YOY%             -48.88% 
=================================================================
 